node.text:
HIM : Babe how much will it take to get started with your plus sized line …. 
ME :  100k ( thinking that will shut him up. I don’t want another project) … 
Him : 👨🏾‍💻done 
i don’t even know what to say I’m still speechless . I worrrrk so hard because I never want to ask anyone or owe anyone.  For this ENERGY on a casual friday when I was just throwing a round about to get him off my case. Someone to believe and take action. 🙍🏽‍♀️#shooketh
